"1433","<body bgcolor=#ffffff style=DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman><br>[LOGO] BBD,LLP CERTIFIED PUBLIC ACCOUNTANTS<br>"
"1434","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt align=center><font style=DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman>REPORT"
"1435","OF INDEPENDENT REGISTERED PUBLIC ACCOUNTING FIRM</font></div>"
"1436","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt><br></div>"
"1437","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt><br></div>"
"1438","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt><br></div>"
"1439","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt align=left><font style=DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman>To"
"1440","the Board of Trustees of Forum Funds</font></div>"
"1441","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt align=left><font style=DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman>and"
"1442","the Shareholders of The BeeHive Fund</font></div>"
"1443","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt><br></div>"
"1444","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt><br></div>"
"1445","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt align=justify><font style=DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman>In"
"1446","planning and performing our audit of the financial statements of The BeeHive"
"1447","Fund (the <font style=DISPLAY: inline; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; FONT-STYLE: italic>Fund</font>), a"
"1448","series of shares of beneficial interest in the Forum Funds, as of December 31,"
"1449","2009 and for the year then ended, in accordance with the standards of the Public"
"1450","Company Accounting Oversight Board (United States), we considered internal"
"1451","control over financial reporting, including controls over safeguarding"
"1452","securities, as a basis for designing our auditing procedures for the purpose of"
"1453","expressing our opinion on the financial statements and to comply with the"
"1454","requirements of Form N-SAR, but not for the purpose of expressing an opinion on"
"1455","the effectiveness of the Fund&#8217;s internal control over financial"
"1456","reporting.&#160;&#160;Accordingly, we express no such opinion.</font></div>"
"1457","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt><br></div>"
"1458","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt align=justify><font style=DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman>The"
"1459","management of The BeeHive Fund is responsible for establishing and maintaining"
"1460","effective internal control over financial reporting.&#160;&#160;In fulfilling"
"1461","this responsibility, estimates and judgments by management are required to"
"1462","assess the expected benefits and related costs of controls.&#160;&#160;A fund&#8217;s"
"1463","internal control over financial reporting is a process designed to provide"
"1464","reasonable assurance regarding the reliability of financial reporting and the"
"1465","preparation of financial statements for external purposes in accordance with"
"1466","generally accepted accounting principles (GAAP). The Fund&#8217;s internal control"
"1467","over financial reporting includes those policies and procedures that (1) pertain"
"1468","to the maintenance of records that, in reasonable detail, accurately and fairly"
"1469","reflect the transactions and dispositions of the assets of the Fund; (2) provide"
"1470","reasonable assurance that transactions are recorded as necessary to permit"
"1471","preparation of the financial statements in accordance with GAAP, and that"
"1472","receipts and expenditures of the Fund are being made only in accordance with"
"1473","authorizations of management and trustees of the Fund; and (3) provide"
"1474","reasonable assurance regarding prevention or timely detection of unauthorized"
"1475","acquisition, use or disposition of the Fund&#8217;s assets that could have a material"
"1476","effect on the financial statements.</font></div>"
"1477","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt><br></div>"
"1478","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt align=justify><font style=DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman>Because"
"1479","of inherent limitations, internal control over financial reporting may not"
"1480","prevent or detect misstatements.&#160;&#160;Also, projections of any evaluation"
"1481","of effectiveness to future periods are subject to the risk that controls may"
"1482","become inadequate because of changes in conditions or that the degree of"
"1483","compliance with the policies or procedures may deteriorate.</font></div>"
"1484","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt><br></div>"
"1485","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt align=justify><font style=DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman>A"
"1486","deficiency in internal control over financial reporting exists when the design"
"1487","or operation of a control does not allow management or employees, in the normal"
"1488","course of performing their assigned functions, to prevent or detect"
"1489","misstatements on a timely basis.&#160;&#160;A material weakness is a deficiency,"
"1490","or combination of deficiencies, in internal control over financial reporting,"
"1491","such that there is a reasonable possibility that a material misstatement of the"
"1492","Fund's annual or interim financial statements will not be prevented or detected"
"1493","on a timely basis.</font></div>"
"1494","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt><br></div>"
"1495","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; MARGIN-LEFT: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0pt align=justify><font style=DISPLAY: inline; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman>Our"
"1496","consideration of the Fund&#8217;s internal control over financial reporting was for"
"1497","the limited purpose described in the first paragraph and would not necessarily"
"1498","disclose all deficiencies in internal control that might be material weaknesses"
"1499","under standards established by the Public Company Accounting Oversight Board"
"1500","(United States).&#160;&#160;However, we noted no deficiencies in the Fund&#8217;s"
"1501","internal control over financial reporting and its operations, including controls"
"1502","for safeguarding securities that we consider to be material weaknesses, as"
"1503","defined above, as of December 31, 2009.</font></div>"
"1504","    <div style=DISPLAY: block; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt><br></div><br>"
